http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/karnataka/Investors%E2%80%99-meet-today/article13976052.ece

A district-level ‘Invest Karnataka-2016’ will be held here on Saturday.It is being organised jointly by the Dharwad district administration, District Industries Centre, and the Department of Handlooms and Textiles.Minister for Mines and Geology and district-in-charge Vinay Kulkarni will inaugurate the event at Hotel Denissons on Gokul Road in Hubballi at 11 a.m. Minister for Small-Scale Industries Satish L. Jarkiholi and Leader of the Opposition in the Legislative Assembly Jagadish Shettar would participate, Joint Director of DIC B.N. Gadag said in a release.